52
00:02:55,693 --> 00:02:59,945
   Knoedler & Company had one   
   of the largest reputations   

53
00:02:59,947 --> 00:03:02,564
       of any art gallery       
         in the country         

54
00:03:02,566 --> 00:03:04,333
           and one of           
     the largest reputations    

