00:03:04,335 --> 00:03:06,735
  of any gallery in the world.  

56
00:03:06,737 --> 00:03:09,555
 Narrator: Its legacy was built 
        by supplying art        

57
00:03:09,557 --> 00:03:13,542
   to Gilded Age tycoons like   
      Cornelius Vanderbilt,     

58
00:03:13,544 --> 00:03:16,879
      John D. Rockefeller,      
        and J.P. Morgan.        

59
00:03:16,881 --> 00:03:20,382
   Over the years it evolved.   
