60
00:03:20,384 --> 00:03:22,801
        It handled modern       
        master paintings.       

61
00:03:22,803 --> 00:03:28,273
And then from around 1970 or so,
    handled contemporary art.   

62
00:03:28,275 --> 00:03:30,425
         And in each one        
        of those domains,       

63
00:03:30,427 --> 00:03:33,862
