104
00:05:25,559 --> 00:05:28,727
      in the United States,     
     some in the art field.     

105
00:05:28,729 --> 00:05:31,013
        Narrator: First,        
     they settle in Houston,    

106
00:05:31,015 --> 00:05:33,098
   where Glafira waits tables   

107
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:36,685
       and Jose finds work      
      as a kitchen helper.      

108
00:05:36,687 --> 00:05:39,321
It takes them little over a year
